channel.title: Cant Get Other People On Server!
channel.description:
Err....couple weeks ago i got a new vista computer....i did all the things i needed to run a server (java, port forwarding, no-ip, the environment thingys, opened the ports) but noone can get on...and it was working fine on my xp computer....
And Yes i did click runserver.bat...
Can somebody tell me whats wrong?? Please and thank you :)[br][br][size=1]Posted on: September 12, 2008, 10:21:25 pm[/size][hr]bump...
